data.description: Amazing Summerlin 4 Bedroom 3 Full Bathroom Pool & Spa Home. Rare Hillcrest Estates Community model. Both a HUGE Master Suite and Bedroom #2 with full bath Downstairs! You can truly live in this home like a 1-story home! No carpet in any bedroom. Dual walk-in closets in master suite. Two more bedrooms upstairs and an Enormous Loft. A/C Compressors/Furnace/Double Ovens/Pool Pump replaced in last 2-3 years. Storage shed pictured conveys with the sale. Palo Verde high school zoned! This home is at the epicenter or restaurants galore and next door to the Lakes, ducks, and geese of Desert Shores. Just 750 feet from 7-Acre The Hills Park featuring an open lawn amphitheater and stage, a children’s play area, two lighted tennis courts, a sand volleyball court, a half baseball court, and seven picnic ramadas. Less than ¼ mile walk to Middle school and Elementary school. Low HOA only $60/month. Great income property if desired! Tenant who just vacated had been paying $3300/month..
